@{
  ViewData["Title"] = "LearnMore";
}
<head>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/LoginPage.css"/>
</head>
<body class=" loginPageBody">
  <h1>Learn More</h1>
  <div class="learnContainer">
    <div class="learnMoreCards">
      <h2 class="removeMargin">What is Digital Banking?</h2>
      <p class="learnMoreText">Digital banking allows you to access and manage your bank account online through your smartphone or computer, anytime, anywhere.</p>
    </div>

	  <div class="learnMoreCards">
		  <h2 class="removeMargin">What is Card Selection?</h2>
		  <p class="learnMoreText">We provide serveral kind of cards as per user need, these range from personal to commercial cards, or order customer cards just for you.</p>
	  </div>
    <div class="learnMoreCards">
      <h2 class="removeMargin">How Secure Is Online Banking?</h2>
      <p class="learnMoreText">We use advanced encryption, secure login, and fraud monitoring to ensure your personal and financial information stays protected at all times.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="learnMoreCards">
      <h2 class="removeMargin">How Can I Open an Account?</h2>
      <p class="learnMoreText">You can easily open an account online by filling a short form and verifying your identity using simple document uploads.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="learnMoreCards">
      <h2 class="removeMargin">Are There Any Monthly Fees?</h2>
      <p class="learnMoreText">Our basic accounts come with no monthly maintenance fees. Special accounts or services may have minimal charges, clearly listed beforehand.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="learnMoreCards">
      <h2 class="removeMargin">Can I Apply for Loans Online?</h2>
      <p class="learnMoreText">Yes, you can apply for personal, home, or education loans directly through our online portal in just a few simple steps.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="learnMoreCards">
      <h2 class="removeMargin">How to Reset My Password?</h2>
      <p class="learnMoreText">If you forget your password, use the "Forgot Password" link on the login page to securely reset it within minutes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="learnMoreCards">
      <h2 class="removeMargin">Is There a Mobile App?</h2>
      <p class="learnMoreText">Yes, our mobile banking app is available for both Android and iOS, offering fast, secure, and full access to your banking services.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="learnMoreCards">
      <h2 class="removeMargin">How Quickly Are Transactions Processed?</h2>
      <p class="learnMoreText">Most transactions happen instantly. Certain transactions like inter-bank transfers may take up to 1–2 business days depending on the method.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="learnMoreCards">
      <h2 class="removeMargin">What If I Lose My Card?</h2>
      <p class="learnMoreText">Immediately block your card through the mobile app or call customer support. We’ll help you issue a replacement quickly.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="learnMoreCards">
      <h2 class="removeMargin">How Can I Contact Support?</h2>
      <p class="learnMoreText">You can reach us via live chat, email, or our 24/7 customer support hotline for any assistance you need.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>

